All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
AdminMenu
The AdminMenu class serves as the main access point for the search and insert forms used by the administrator of the database.
Course
The Course class is the abstract representation of a course.
CourseInsertForm
The CourseInsertForm class creates a form for inserting a new course record to the database.
CourseRegistrationForm
The CourseRegistrationForm class creates a form for registering a student to a course.
CourseSearchForm
The CourseSearchForm class creates a form for searching a specific course record in the database.
CourseUpdateDeleteForm
The CourseUpdateDeleteForm class creates a form for updating and/or deleting a course record in the database.
DBUtil
The DBUtil class is responsible for establishing a connection to the database.
LoginRegisterForm
The LoginRegisterForm class creates the login form for entering into the system.
Main
The Main class is the driver class of the application.
PeriodType
The PeriodType enum class contains a standardized list of academic periods.
SecUtil
The SecUtil class contains methods for encrypting and de-crypting operations.
StudentInsertForm
The StudentInsertForm class creates a form for inserting a new student record to the database.
StudentSearchForm
The StudentSearchForm class creates a form for searching a specific student record in the database.
StudentUpdateDeleteForm
The StudentUpdateDeleteForm class creates a form for updating and/or deleting a student record in the database.
Teacher
The Teacher class is the abstract representation of a teacher.
TeacherInsertForm
The TeacherInsertForm class creates a form for adding a new teacher record to the database.
TeacherSearchForm
The TeacherSearchForm class creates a form for searching a specific teacher record in the database.
TeacherUpdateDeleteForm
The TeacherUpdateDeleteForm class creates a form for updating/deleting a teacher record in the database.
UpdatePasswordForm
The UpdatePasswordForm class creates a form for updating the password of a student user.
UserDeleteForm
The UserDeleteForm class creates a form for deleting a user record from the database.
UserMenu
The class serves as the main access point to the CourseRegistrationForm and UpdatePasswordForm classes.
UserSearchForm
The UserSearchForm class creates a form for searching a specific user record in the database.
